  <text>
    <body>
      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>Sweet High</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>…I never knew</l>
          <l>I could smile just like you</l>
          <l>Then hand me lovely lies, ten thousand joys will rise</l>
          <l>it's God's worst love</l>
          <l>Be, my pretty blue</l>
          <l>Cover me with all of you</l>
          <l>Put on your pretty face, fix me I'm a mess</l>
          <l>Save me</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>And it's driving me insane this old urge to see your face</l>
          <l>Aching through my loving blood again</l>
          <l>You are so beautiful addictive beautiful</l>
          <l>My sweet high</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>I…I never knew</l>
          <l>I'll die each night for your divine shine to be bright</l>
          <l>Light up my face again</l>
          <l>Ring them old bells again</l>
          <l>Make it right</l>
          <l>We ..we know you well that sweet smile can turn to hell</l>
          <l>And now your dance is done</l>
          <l>You had your little fun</l>
          <l>But no one leaves</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
    </body>
